<i>noun</i>: 횡포 [횡포/휑포], 학정 [학쩡], 폭정 [폭쩡], 전제주의 [전제주의/전제주이] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>횡포 [횡포/휑포]</dt><br>
<dd>tyranny; despotism</dd><br>
<dd>제멋대로 굴며 매우 난폭함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of acting as one pleases and being extremely violent.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>학정 [학쩡]</dt><br>
<dd>tyranny; dictatorship; despotism</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 모질고 잔인한 정치.</dd><br>
<dd>An extremely heartless and cruel rule by a king, government, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>폭정 [폭쩡]</dt><br>
<dd>tyranny; dictatorship; despotism</dd><br>
<dd>매우 사납고 악한 정치.</dd><br>
<dd>An extremely heartless and cruel rule by a king, government, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>전제주의 [전제주의/전제주이]</dt><br>
<dd>absolutism; despotism</dd><br>
<dd>국가의 권력을 개인이 휘어잡아 법률이나 국민의 뜻과 상관없이 마음대로 실시하는 정치의 시행을 주장하는 정치 사상.</dd><br>
<dd>A political ideology holding that one individual should have all the power over a nation and impose his/her political ideas on his/her people with no regard for their will or existing laws.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>